node.text: I remember when magazines would not want to book me for a job because I’m too glam😕...But, @kyliejenner has always fought for me so hard! And has always had so much faith and trust in my artistry and pushed me to be greater than! Now I’ve lost count of how many covers we’ve done together!! I love you endlessly 🤍🙏🏽 dreams really do come true! My story with Kylie really is a true testament to the fact that you never know who is watching. Nearly 8 years ago I was just a little boy in Brooklyn, New York with a dream! But that little boy had so much persistence and determination to be somebody and to get noticed! I reached out to everyone because I knew that I had nothing to lose and everything to gain!!! There were a lot of no replies, which obviously didn’t feel the best but still didn’t deteriorate me! But there were some that did and for those I’m forever grateful! Specifically @lillyghalichi my fairy glam mom🧚🏼! After working with her for a while in LA and New York kylie noticed my work on social media and reached out to me through DM!! This day forever changed my life! And I will forever be grateful! But my point of the story is dreams really do come true and perseverance is key! It’s so important to remember that everyone’s timeline is so different and everyone’s journey to success is also so different. Never compare yourself to anyone else that is so toxic and unhealthy and will never help you get to where you want. Focus all your energy and growing yourself and keeping your eyes on your goals! 🏆🙏🏽🤍 #godisgood

Omgg😱😫😱😭😭 we just launched! I’m crying!! Sales are live Now! you can shop at Morphe.com (link in bio) and In store at @morphebrushes and online @ultabeauty, @sephoracanada @meccabeauty !!! Make sure to use code “Ariel “ at check out to save some money on your purchase!! This such a surreal moment and I cannot believe it’s happening!! Thank you to everyone for your support and I hope you guys enjoy these brush sets as much as I have!

 All of my brushes are tested and perfected by me and come in two luxurious sets: The SIGNATURE LOOK 12-piece face & eye brush set ($98) and The SIGNATURE EYES 8-piece eye brush set ($48us).
 

Shop the collection NOW on morphe.com + Morphe stores, @meccabeauty, @ultabeauty (online), @sephoacanada (online)
